        public FinishProcessingNodeEvent(Object source,
                                 BAPNode node,
                                 double nodeBound,
                                 double nodeValue,
                                 int numberOfCGIterations,

                                 long pricingSolveTime,
                                 int nrGeneratedColumns)
        Creates a new FinishProcessingNodeEvent
        Parameters:
        source - Generator of this event
        node - node which has been solved
        nodeBound - Bound on the node which has been solved
        nodeValue - Objective value of the node which has been solved. When solved to optimality, nodeBound and nodeValue should be equal
        numberOfCGIterations - Number of CG iterations it took to solve the node
        masterSolveTime - Total amount of time spent on solving the master problems
        pricingSolveTime - Total amount of time spent on solving the pricing problems
        nrGeneratedColumns - Total number of columns generated
